The diarrhea lasted all weekend thinking was going to subside. It did not. I went urgent care three days later with them telling me it was going to subside! It did not ! I went to the er the next day with them keeping me being diagnosed with inflammation of the colon , colonitis! It was a nightmare in intravenous and antibiotics the whole time. I was discharged after 8 days and I still have slight diarrhea! I would not wish this condition in my worst enemy. I thought I was going to die!!! I urge anyone do not eat from this establishment!!!!
